title_full:
Kali Malone

              —
              All Life Long (for organ)
            
              (Ideologic Organ)
label: for organ
description:
Stephen O’Malley’s Ideologic Organ herald a new Kali Malone album with the pipe organ fanfare of its lead single.

‘All Life Long (for organ)’ unusually, for Kali’s music, emphasises melody over all as it traces a hopeful higher register cadence subtly countered with melancholy bass motif, warmly brought to life and suspended in the air by O’Malley’s production. The album 'All Life Long' is due in Feb 2024.

title_full:
Burial and Kode9

              —
              Phoneglow / Eyes Go Blank
            
              (Hyperdub)
label: Hyperdub
description:
Hyperdub mark 20 years of UK bassbin domination with proper perlers by Burial & Kode9 on a classic ‘Untrue’ tip with a recombinant hardcore footwork flex.

Hyperdub have captivated us ever since Kode9's momentous flip of Prince's 'Sign O The Times,' b/w a proto-dubstep template back in 2004.
